'''Stormtrooper rations''' were canned, self-warming [[Food rations|rations]] issued to [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Stormtrooper/Legends|stormtroopers]] during their service to the Empire. They contained a heat mod with a shelf life of about twenty [[standard year/Legends|years]].<ref name="Dark Forces: Jedi Knight">''[[Dark Forces: Jedi Knight]]''</ref>

The grayish, gooey substance was horribly bland, but it met the nutritional requirements of a typical stormtrooper. Each canister of stormtrooper rations bore the Imperial stamp of approval, an assurance that the rations were safe to eat and quite nutritious. They were commonly found on a [[Stormtrooper armor/Legends|stormtrooper armor's]] utility belt.

